Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Hinckley insanity defence
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043ww1d
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Aug 1982
Lawyers unhappy as insanity defence saves would-be presidential assassin Hinckley. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less